    "description": "The Gasoline Gypsies Game is a retro 2-D action platform game. Play as Caleb, Steve, Joe, and Neal as they try to make it to the top. <br><br>As a member of the Gasoline Gypsies you will run, jump, and rock your way through various levels. Find hidden items and power-ups along the way. Use your instruments to defeat opponents. You will encounter broken strings, zombie tuners, deranged groupies, and more on your way to the stage. At the end of each level you will face off with a rival group.<br><br>Listen to 8-bit renditions of original Gasoline Gypsies music as you travel across Michigan. On your adventure you will unlock levels, costumes, mini games and more. Compete for dominance on the online leaderboard or team up with a friend for local co-op. The Gasoline Gypsies Game is a colorful non violent game intended for all ages.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>14 Levels &amp; Bosses<br>3 Unique Power-Ups<br>2 player co-op (with 2nd gamepad)<br>Sound Test<br>Difficulty Settings<br>Online Leaderboard<br>Unlockable Achievements, Costumes, &amp; Mini Games",
